local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["kinship"]={"kinship","['kɪnʃɪp]","['kɪnʃɪp]","n.血缘关系",'n.血缘关系,亲属关系','A large citizens\' organization based on kinship, constituting the largest political subdivision of an ancient Greek city-state.','宗族是一种基于亲戚关系的巨大的市民组织，它组成了古希腊城邦的最大的政治分支。','Even after meeting only once, they felt a kinship.','他们虽然只见了一面，但已是一见如故了。'}
